pkgc:ID_1307979835 a skos:Concept ;
    dc:date "2020-10-31"^^xsd:date ;
    skos:prefLabel "Michael has a unique skill set at the intersection of linguistics, data science, crowdsourcing operation, and tooling UI development. This enabled him to effectively run an applied research program that hired, trained, and managed crowd workers to perform advanced linguistic data collection at scale to power novel machine learning algorithms within Google Research and Machine Intelligence. Such work typically required advanced linguistic knowledge to perform, but Michael had insights on how to translate such domain expert tasks into crowdsource-able composable tasks. Meticulous but never losing sight of the overall goal, Michael took the research from its conceptual stage of problem definition all the way to the implementation of task interfaces and the management of the crowdsourcing operation itself. He made impactful contributions to advances in Linguistics and NLP at Google over the last five years that I've known him. I fully and without hesitation recommend Michael, and if I ever start another research program in Linguistics I would try to hire him again in a heartbeat. See less" ;
    pkg:sourceMap "data.mm" .

